ures\nof entanglement-based quantum technology room temperature sensors,\nre-envisioning YIG as a modern quantum material.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 2 Feb 2020 17:59:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 23 Feb 2020 22:14:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 18 Sep 2020 11:58:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-21"}
