on. The set of scaling-laws we\nderived can be broadly applied to cool stars from the PMS to the end of the MS,\nand allow for a stellar wind modelling consistent with all the observational\nconstraints available to date.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Feb 2020 13:06:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-01"}
