 wave forces\nresponsible for wave setup generation across the surf zone. Overall, the\nresults reveal how the mesh-free SPH approach can accurately reproduce the\ndetailed wave breaking processes with comparable skill to state-of-the-art\nmesh-based Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD) models, and thus can be applied\nto provide valuable new physical insight into surf zone dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Feb 2020 15:34:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-04"}
